Lots of fun yet salty nights in college playing this game. Alcohol and League just don't generally mix. I originally made this account just to play drunk games in bronze. Couple of chat restrictions for it along with ruining games for teammates. 

But on the bright side been sober 2 years now and haven't had a chat restrictions since. 

Remember kids, drink responsibly. And yes, there is life without alcohol and even without League {{sticker:slayer-jinx-wink}}
